{"tid":2496862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"克欽軍大捷　緬甸軍方遭遇嚴重損失　兩個營重創","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T06:30:18.000Z","uid":261647,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a14ed8f8682ba01bdb4f2fc429cc40f2d1b7f8c4","tid":2496862,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LetsPlayWargame/posts/237600814770577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLetsPlayWargame%2Fposts%2F237600814770577&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d22ed07b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/LetsPlayWargame/posts/237600814770577</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmctM1kM3LhUR1jtqRkPW4UECX3wnexzRM7tq2u2wmdDXi?filename=5qJ0a15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qJ0a15.jpg&h=25d5c94b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：Let&rsquo;s Play Wargame<br />\n<br />\n#克欽軍大捷 緬甸軍方遭遇重大損失 兩個營重創<br />\n<br />\n近日，緬甸「國防軍」召集大批兵力向此前被克欽獨立軍（KIA）攻克的戰略高地Alaw Bum發起進攻，意圖攻擊30公裡外的克欽軍總部。在這次戰役中，緬甸國防軍出動至少兩架戰機支援，不過克欽邦軍一直堅守陣地。據說，軍政府的部隊損失慘重，其中包括一個步兵營的指揮官。是次戰役中，國防軍第387步兵營遭重創，包括營長在內的至少39人被擊斃，被迫退出戰鬥；第320步兵營則被全殲，死亡100餘人。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Myanmar Now<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.myanmar-now.org/en/news/myanmar-military-suffers-heavy-casualties-in-bid-to-recapture-hill-base-from-kia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myanmar-now.org%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fmyanmar-military-suffers-heavy-casualties-in-bid-to-recapture-hill-base-from-kia&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=c2bbb59d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.myanmar-now.org/en/news/myanmar-military-suffers-heavy-casualties-in-bid-to-recapture-hill-base-from-kia</a>"},{"pid":"4e906b4c2256ca60ba8f8c8ee69c14d049ac4f4a","tid":2496862,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第320步兵營則被全殲，死亡100餘人。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46cab1808105960867852d39ff1c8ad1376369e","tid":2496862,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"政府軍仲有幾多人等死？"},{"pid":"adcca228444ea450577300ad60953865d6bc4765","tid":2496862,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"一個營都幾百人 死100個點全殲"},{"pid":"3643f06d401b9c499d037b1be40be48be3ce99cf","tid":2496862,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:23:51.000Z","msg":"地頭蟲佔盡地利？"},{"pid":"fbda453d0bf9beadb50a3ee70ff672e5967967e7","tid":2496862,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adcca228444ea450577300ad60953865d6bc4765","tid":2496862,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"一個營都幾百人 死100個點全殲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:25:46.000Z","msg":"咁佢個營可能死淨100幾個呢...死下少d死下少d，又冇人加入"},{"pid":"339bee8fcfef20a6c15b7b5a817142fe9db92706","tid":2496862,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"作者： lets play wargame<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846bc31255613036b912f03f779d65d11e917305","tid":2496862,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"越南大戰已經out了<br />\n<br />\n而家街機應該出緬甸大戰"},{"pid":"3cb481f0c54f98f15a610d5360748796ae15a491","tid":2496862,"uid":40398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adcca228444ea450577300ad60953865d6bc4765","tid":2496862,"uid":176447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"一個營都幾百人 死100個點全殲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"死都1xx, 仲未計傷同失蹤<br />\n都無哂戰